reviews_data.review_text: We enjoyed our Sunday visit to Biggby for an Americano & wife had a double espresso.  Both were delicious.  We each loved our warm muffins too.  Food menu is limited, could offer croissants or other pastries.  They do offer bagel and egg sandwiches Atmosphere is nice with a couple comfy chairs.

Went for the first time and the foot and coffee was so good. The service was also really good.

I got the iced teddy bear latte & my bf got one of the fruit smoothies
I visited this coffee shop for the first time. The two ladies there were super sweet and friendly. It was the birthday for the company.. Definitely going back. Food was great as well.
The drinks at this coffee shop are great. They have multiple sugar free options available, including a “Nutty Buddy” drink which was delicious. The staff are efficient and professional.
I love the chocolate milk

Young guy operating the drive thru is super helpful and kind. Dude also looks like Chris Klein from American Pie as well lol

My cold brew was solid. Coffee options for days. Will come back and try food options next time
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks so much for the awesome review! We’re so glad you loved the cold brew—it's one of our favorites too. Can’t wait to see you again soon for your next coffee fix! 🥧🍎  #BIGGBYLove

reviews_data.review_text: Super cute inside, really clean also. The workers were all so kind and the service was great. The coffee and matcha were amazing, we also got a cookie milkshake for our little and he loved it. They were also able to make us a bacon egg and cheese even though it’s not on the menu. I have nothing but great things to say about Biggby Coffee. Also loved the shark week decor and drinks.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you, Riley! We REALLY appreciate the encouragement, and it's customers like you that make us love our jobs in a Bigg way!

reviews_data.review_text: Good coffee and breakfast options, and great service.
reviews_data.owner_answer: So appreciated!  Thanks Nathan for the kind review!

reviews_data.review_text: Overpriced coffee, Expect to pay at least $7 for a Dunkin-esque drink. The service isn’t horrible, but it’s not great. They need to work on improving their process to be more efficient and lowering the prices.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Hi Abbiie,

Thanks for taking the time to leave a review. While we’re always open to honest feedback, this one doesn’t quite match the experience most of our guests have.

Our drink prices are clearly posted, with plenty of options well under $7. Our team works hard to deliver great service every day, so we’re genuinely curious what you ordered. Unfortunately, there’s not much detail here, especially on the size drink you ordered, or whether there were extra add-ins that could have bumped up the price.

Just a heads-up... if something’s ever off, our shift leaders or managers are always happy to make it right on the spot. It doesn’t seem like we got that chance this time.

To anyone else reading, don’t just take our word for it. Stop by and see why so many folks choose us every day.

reviews_data.review_text: Great food and coffee , friendly service and great prices !
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for this lovely review. We really appreciate it!

reviews_data.review_text: Great friendly staff, quick service, atmosphere was great all around.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Erika, thanks so much for this kind review!  We love our staff.  They are the reason for our success!

reviews_data.review_text: Love BIGBY.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
BIGGBY Loves you BACK!
🥰🤗🥰🤗

reviews_data.review_text:
I love coming here! My drink is perfect every time, even with all of my modifications.
I can barely go 2 days without one of the chocolate chip cookies & blueberry muffins, it’s a problem…
Very clean environment, the music varies day to day, but always bangers. Love it there 🩷
Delicious coffee and the BEST staff!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
We do love our coffee, but we love our staff and customers even more!  We believe that BIGGBY MAKES IT BETTER.

We so appreciate this awesome review!!!
🥳👏🏻🎉🥳🙌

reviews_data.review_text: My experience at this  Biggby location have always been nothing but pleasurable! The staff are super nice and prompt! Service with a smile!
I love Biggby coffee!! I’m from Michigan and am so thankful that we have one here!  I love the sugar free mocha and the baristas are so great!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for the five stars! We are thrilled that you love us:) Cheers to the sugar-free mocha lattes:)

reviews_data.review_text:
The workers here are always friendly and courteous and make sure that you get your coffee just how you like it!! Biggby may be a chain coffee shop but they are exemplary. The coffee is also amazing every time I come! Their lattes & cold brews just rock. What else can I say?!

Edit: Just have to add - LOVE y’all Biggby!!!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Rachel, thank you so very much for these kind words. We appreciate you taking the time to recognize our outstanding baristas publicly. And you know what? They are genuine and they really do care for our customers:)

reviews_data.review_text: Hit or miss days not everyone can make the drinks
I only drink plain hot coffee and this place is more styled to the dramatic drinks. There is great coffee around Charlotte and I’m sure people who like sugary coffee like this place.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Have you tried our French roast or an Americano? The best around, that's why we bought the place:)

reviews_data.review_text: We didn’t drive-through for 20 minutes with only two cars in front of me
the batistas are always really nice :) yummy food and coffee
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for kind words and encouragement!

reviews_data.review_text: Over priced. My sandwich was soggy and the coffee tasted burnt. The service was alright. Not really a place I want to give a second chance.
Great coffee, nice that they have so many unique flavors.  I like the music too.  Overall refreshing change from the normal ho-hum coffee shops that charge 40% more!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for your kind words! We love to read encouragement:) Come back in and let us get to know you:)

reviews_data.review_text: I just wanted to leave a quick review to express how much I enjoy starting my day at this coffee shop. I've been a regular for a few weeks now, popping in a few times a week for my morning coffee fix. It's simply a pleasant and welcoming atmosphere to kickstart the day. On top of that, I had a fantastic experience with Stephanie. I was feeling adventurous and wanted to try something new, but I was struggling to make a decision. Stephanie was incredibly helpful and recommended the Irish coffee. It was absolutely delicious and the perfect way to begin the week! Thanks, Stephanie, and I'll definitely be back soon!

review_questions.Recommended dishes: Biggby Best Coffee Beans - 12 Oz Pre-Ground Bag, Assorted Muffins

reviews_data.owner_answer: Yep! Stephanie is one of the greatest humans in the world! She has a big heart. We consider her an asset to our coffee shop. Thanks for taking the time to share your encouragement!

reviews_data.review_text: Cute place - great service, good food and drink!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for taking the time to leave us an outstanding encouragement! It is much appreciated as we are real people working hard behind the counter:)

reviews_data.review_text: Coffee was amazing, wonderful ambience, and the staff was really friendly. A nice cozy place.
DELICIOUS!!!! My wife and I really like your coffee.
Service was very slow.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hum... I wonder what happened this day. We are usually quick. Please give us another try:)

reviews_data.review_text: My husband and I love your coffee!! Thank you for the yums!! :) May the Lord God Almighty bless you richly :)
reviews_data.owner_answer: We are blessed! Thanks for stopping by and may you, too, know the Lord's richest blessing.

reviews_data.review_text: I recently found Biggby Coffee on DoorDash and have been OBSESSED since. Embarrassingly I’ve order 3x in the past week but the food and coffee is soooo good! I get the Sweet Foam Lucky Charm Cold Brew and the Turkey Havarti bagel and it’s a 10/10 every time! They even write sweet notes on your order!
reviews_data.owner_answer: AWWW. Thank you for taking the time to leave us a review! Glad you love your specialty drink and bragel:) We also appreciate great customers!

reviews_data.review_text: I absolutely love this place! ALWAYS great service & coffee. My new go to!
If I have one complaint they need to get their coffee hotter. It's never hot enough. Always having to take it to a microwave. Other than that tastes great.
Excellent service and delicious coffee. They were happy to fill my reusable coffee cup instead of a paper cup.
Stopped by here real quick because I was early for my nail appointment. Fantastic!!! Nice surprise.
Found a hair in my bagel, when I asked for it to be remade John told me that was not possible and said that I put the hair in my own food.
Went in they changed their hours are I open till 7 Monday thru Sat and only till 6 on Sunday so hopefully my edit worked
Very kind and fast!
Coffee was great. Staff was super friendly.
We went for the first time and each got a coffee drink and shared a Bagel sandwich. The coffee, sandwich, and service were all great and we will go again soon!
So nice to have a good alternative to Starbucks.

I’ve only ordered delivery - however, these bagels are SO good. The customer service is also great, I love when employees write notes for the customers. When I ordered something on DoorDash, they immediately called me to let me know they were out of an ingredient, gave me all my other options, and changed my order for me without me having to lift a finger. I may be developing a Biggby addiction.

I was recently there and I live close to the area about six months ago. I know the owners John and Melissa and new associates were very friendly fast day get everybody’s orders in a timely manner and the coffee is probably some of the best coffee out there it’s better than the other companies like Starbucks and other companies
Great coffee, and customer service. Very friendly nice staff.
Absolutely so cute and the staff is so helpful! Would go every day ❤️

Dead dull place with dead dull employees. Ordered a regular coffee and staff had to make a new pot but never said anything. Only knew because I saw them making a pot and figured since they hadn’t given me my coffee…then was given it without a thank you or apology for wait. There’s also a lack of space and seating. And where in the hell is the sugar? Was going to sit down and work but horrible experience changed my dine in to a to go.

I ordered a Peppermint Stick Mocha Latte and it was very good. I had it made with oat milk. Loved the candy cane crunchies on top of the whip. Also, the hubby bought a coffee and they have the best refill prices and are environmentally friendly. Also, comfortable inside. Employee was super friendly.

Absolutely delicious coffee. Get a frozen caramel marvel latte. You will never be disappointed.

Friendly staff as well!

review_questions.Recommended dishes: Butter Bear, Teddy Bear, Frozen Teddy Bear, Caramel Marvel

reviews_data.review_text: Biggby Coffee is my families favorite neighborhood coffee shop! Service is always friendly, the store is always clean, and the coffee is DELICIOUS! My favorite is a hot Butter Bear Latte and a sausage, egg, and cheese bragel. Sooo good!
Food was okay at best. Coffee was okay as well. I would go back if in the area at breakfast time
Such a great local business!!!

review_questions.Recommended dishes: Butter Bear, Assorted Muffins, Sausage Egg and Cheese, Caramel Marvel

reviews_data.review_text: How have I never heard of this place?! We wanted a pick me up and quick snack so I googled coffee in the local area. Not only is their Wednesday happy hour a GREAT deal, but the drinks/food were delicious and the staff were so very sweet! My kids gobbled down their massive muffins too fast for me to snap a picture and the seasonal waffle sandwich was a treat! Definitely try the golden honey drink or the matcha iced latte. Both yummy choices!
reviews_data.owner_answer: THANK YOU SO MUCH! This is entirely encouraging to us that you took the time to share.

reviews_data.review_text: Always amazing! I go out of my way just to go here 💜💜💜
reviews_data.owner_answer: You have really encouraged us. Thank you for taking the time to share this with us! We are so proud of our staff!

reviews_data.review_text: The ladies here, and their customer service, are fantastic - this place is always super friendly!
Always very friendly staff & great coffee + food! Plus my dog loves their pup cups :)

Probably my fifth visit.   All have been the same.   Very helpful, great attitudes, always CLEAN.  THEY told me about today’s special, saved me some money on drinks for our office team.   They have a special value every weekday (photo).     Simply, it was just a great visit.   Seems like it’s getting harder and harder to find a simple great visit.    They are 5 for 5 for me.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for your encouragement! We can't wait to serve up drinks for your staff again!

reviews_data.review_text: I stayed there for 2 days and I went to BIGGBY Coffee for 2 days. It was soooo good!!!!I wish there could be a store near where I live.

I’ve been to this location about a dozen times, I like the coffee but we always have issues with the pricing and service. Every time we order, the prices seem to be different. You never pay the menu price for your drink. The up charges are not consistent and I never know how much things cost. We went inside because the drive through service is extremely slow and you are told so wait when you reach the speaker. We ordered the special on the board(no prices). The drink was $9 but there was a $1 up charge for oatmilk when they offered whole milk. They charge you for whole milk and said there’s no button for it. I really feel like something is shady here or the POS system is impossible to navigate. Also, the time before I ordered 2 drinks on the buy one get one for $1 day. They used my free drink reward for the second drink. The problems list is too long for the coffee.
Love this BIGGBY location.
Kelsey and a friendly young gentleman took excellent care of me while I was in today.  The shop has a clean and welcoming atmosphere, and my drink was delicious!
Coffee is ok but never try the GOOD TO GO at this place because they will just give you couple cups of coffee ONLY so not worth it

Omg i love this place. I don’t even drink coffee that much but since they moved in to town I’m there two to three times a week. I love the frozen teddy bear or butter bear and the everything turkey cheese bagel is delicious. On top of that the customer service has always been above and beyond. You have a great team working there.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks, Jamie. We appreciate your commitment to our store. And we really do have the very best customers:)

reviews_data.review_text: Cute little walkable spot for McCullough neighborhood!
Expensive.   But very good.  Clean

review_questions.Parking options: Free parking lot, Free parking garage

reviews_data.review_text: Wanted to say that Melissa at Biggby Coffee in Pineville cares about giving back to her local community as she donates to help out a little league team in Pineville thru Hope Soccer.  On behalf of Hope Soccer, we are very grateful for the impact Biggby has on our local kids! As a consumer of any service, I know that I look for businesses who are involved in their local community, such as Biggby Coffee! Also, I can tell you personally that their coffee and their bagel sandwiches are great!  Highly recommend!
Supper good whenever we go out of town we look for a biggby coffee it never disappoints this location was definitely my favorite staff was amazing thank you so much for everything 😊

Visited recently because I got an ad on Facebook and it’s so close to my house. I always love trying new coffee shops even though it can be hit or miss. This was definitely a hit though! I love that my latte has a nice sweet flavor while also being able to taste the espresso. I think they do a fantastic job balancing the sweetener to coffee ratio. I ordered a caramel marshmallow iced latte and loved it.

My boyfriend stopped in to grab us coffee again today and I got the same drink, and it tasted the same as when I got it the other day so they’re definitely consistent. We also tried the donut holes last time we visited, and those were great too.

The staff was super friendly and chatty with customers which is always nice to see anywhere you go. We will definitely come again in the future and make this our new go to spot.
Had a very pleasant experience visiting Biggby Coffee this morning! Customer service was phenomenal and very quick. The coffee itself was even better. Will definitely be coming back soon!

Ordered through DoorDash and was pleasantly surprised. The cold brew was incredible and the bagel was just as amazing, if not better! I love that they serve their bagels into the afternoon, most places don’t do that.

Disappointed with the coffee at the Waffle House, I headed here and spent an hour this morning sipping away at a small coffee that was actually the size of a small oil drum while I wrote a couple Yelp reviews. There's a very comfy single-seat booth in the back that was pretty darned awesome with a power outlet and a nice view of the comings and goings.

The coffee was excellent and the space was lovely.

review_questions.null: Vegetarian options, Dietary restrictions, Parking, Kid-friendliness, Wheelchair accessibility

reviews_data.review_text: This Bigby is located near my house and I can walk from my house to this place. I’ve been coming here almost over a year now since it was first open back in February 2023 the price is affordable and will meet your budget needs like other coffee chains.

So many new faces they don’t seemed like they are getting proper training…

Edit-  I had never said that the service, food or drinks were bad I just said that there was a lot of new faces!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hailey, we are saddened to read this review. Perhaps our team had an off day, it does happen. But in general, I love my baristas and think they are the absolute best staff to work with. Barista service can be challenging, working to perfect 300+ drinks. We hope you'll be gracious and give our coffee shop another try.

reviews_data.review_text: Best coffee. Best customer service  By far my favorite place for coffee. Different special every day.
Super friendly staff, great drinks, and good value.

review_questions.Recommended dishes: Golden Honey, Bagel & Cream Cheese, Turkey Havarti

reviews_data.review_text: Picked up an order from here
Great Drinks! I ordered a Carmel sweet cream cold brew and it was delicious! The staff is super friendly and quick!
The Cinnabuzz Matcha Latte was a tasty twist to traditional Matcha! Yum!! The staff was delightful and service was quick!

We stopped here after visiting the nearby flea market, the experience was all around MID. The time it took to prepare beverages (4) was absurd and when we got them they didn't even taste like anything 🤔.

Very slow service, and they were not packed at all. I would definitely not go here during a rush hour time or if I had something else to do immediately after, which one of the people in my party ended up being late for work because we didn't know it would take upwards of 35mins to get a drink.

The flavor just wasn't there either.
The BEST cold foam ever. Very sweet staff and I’m so glad that they have weekly deals!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for the nice review! We are super proud of our baristas!

reviews_data.review_text: Biggby coffee in pineville is one of our families favorites! The staff is wonderful and the coffee tastes great.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks Abby! We love seeing your family in our store and we can't wait to serve you all again soon!

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee and some yummy doughnuts
reviews_data.owner_answer: We're so happy to hear you love our coffee & doughnut holes! They're a Biggby Fanatic favorite for a reason :)

reviews_data.review_text: Always an awesome treat I get 2-3 times a week, excellent staff and smiles all around, love biggby coffee !!

Tired of weak Dunkin? Weary of burnt Starbucks? Biggby coffee is fresh and smooth! They carry everything from traditional blends to very creative latte drinks. The atmosphere is welcoming and friendly - if a bit small. Highly recommend!
This place is incredible! Great customer service, great environment, and super clean store! The drinks are incredible and always so yummy! Support your local business!!

I've been to this location multiple times, and the menu looks so exciting with multiple flavor options and most of them available in sugar free. I love creative mixes for my lattes, but it always falls very flat here. At Starbucks, they lack variety especially in sugar-free, but when they put syrup in you can taste it. You can taste it too much and as a matter of fact at Starbucks I always tell them to do half of the amount of syrup they normally do, so I'm not a person that likes an over sugary and syrupy drink. I'm writing this review because at this location, even though they have such cool interesting sounding drinks, you can't taste the syrup at all. It tastes like drinking espresso with warmed milk and a little tiny bit of sweetener, but no flavor whatsoever. I guess if I return to try their coffee, I'm going to have to ask for additional pumps and then watch it be too sweet would be my luck. Again, I'm really happy with all the flavor combinations offered here but you can't taste it.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Ginger. Thank you for the feedback. Our baristas are very knowledgable about our menu and different syrups and would love to help you find the perfect balance between sweetness and flavor. If you stop in again, feel free to ask about a certain latte's sweetness or how the barista would make it for themselves! We'd love the chance to wow you with our variety of flavors :)

reviews_data.review_text: Great place for coffee, and very friendly staff.
Great coffee!
Fabulous customer service. We were first timers and the young lady explained the different drinks and answered all of our questions. Definitely will be back and will spread the word.

Stopped by here on the way home from work mainly because of the location and drive thru option. I ordered an iced vanilla latte and I wasn’t a fan. Their espresso is a little too strong for my taste. It wasn’t a good blend for me. I’m not gonna write off the place because some people like strong coffee, it just wasn’t for me!
reviews_data.owner_answer: Terri, thanks for stopping by. We would love for you to give us a 2nd chance. May I recommend next time getting one less shot of espresso in your iced vanilla latte? We would love to keep trying until we get it perfect for you. Just ask the barista how many shots come in the size of your latte and make the adjustment:) We do care.

reviews_data.review_text: The coffee is great and the staff is even nicer. Really a great place to see how a business should be ran
reviews_data.owner_answer: This is quite a compliment! Thank you, sincerely! We love our brew crew, and they work very hard; they genuinely care about people!

reviews_data.review_text: The drink I had was amazing!! Hands down better than most. The Asiago bagel with cream cheese was tough to chew and fairly dry. I wish I could have had more cream cheese because I could barely taste it. From now on I will just order the frozen coffee
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for the feedback. This cream cheese business is no joke. It's surprising how strongly some customers feel about cream cheese:) Some are disturbed at the very idea of adding cream cheese to a sausage and cheese bagel, and some want extra and then some! So please come back and try again, and let us customize it to your liking. Our asiago is very popular right now!

reviews_data.review_text: Great Food, Great Coffee. Wonderful doordash experience with a personal note inside.
Friendly staff, exceptionally clean store. Conveniently located minutes from Carolina Place Mall.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thank you for this review! We LOVE coffee. We LOVE clean, too:) We want to meet you when you come back:)

reviews_data.review_text: Clean, modern, bright coffee shop with very friendly staff and decent coffee. Has a drive through also.

So, this is only my second review ever, I don’t usually do this but it’s almost been a year they’ve been open and they deserve this! I’ve gone to Biggby for years back home (was so excited when they opened here!!) and have been in love with their sweet foam cold brew which is the best ever made, hands down! What makes the experience the best is the people here. John and Melissa are amazing and go above and beyond to make sure everyone is happy and enjoying their coffee (even when I can be a pain!) and you build a relationship with the rest of the staff when you go every day. They treat you like family and you know each other on a first name basis, which you don’t get very often in the world. Everyone I bring coffee to at my work absolutely loves their coffee and they all look forward to $5 Friday! I would give them 100 stars if I could but I’m limited to 5 so I will end with this… I love Biggby coffee no matter where I go but what makes this one special and the absolute best is the owners and the people who are making our coffee everyday. I appreciate y'all and thank y'all for everything!
I love getting coffee here before going to the Miller flea market next to it
reviews_data.owner_answer: Excellent! We are glad to be a convenient shop for you to help you enjoy your weekends:)

reviews_data.review_text:
We had an overall good experience here. The place is clean and tidy. Very minimalist approach. Coffee specialty drinks were a wild array of offerings. They offered a strawberry coffee and it was not good at all. It was unexpectedly bitter.

The chai is great with oat milk. The teddy bear, half-swedt, was good, according to my wife. We haven't purchased food here yet, so I can't speak for that.

CX service was excellent! Everyone was friendly, attentive, and patient. Drinks came up quickly, too!
Had a coffee and bagel very good and very welcoming staff will be back!

Great coffee not too sweet but still yummy

Great service with a smile...

Hubs and I came in and had no idea what to order huge menu with the ability to customize your drink. And they aren't snobs like some other places here in Charlotte.

Friendly faces in a quiet but cozy atmosphere! Def coming back
Love the Citrus Snow Latte
reviews_data.owner_answer: wonderful! we have just a bit more of this seasonal product if you want to sneak over again for one last citrus snow;)

reviews_data.review_text: Ordered a peppermint stick mocha and it has no coffee flavor, all milk with a hint of peppermint. Coffee was disgusting and I ended up pouring it out. 1st and last visit
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Autumn! I'm not sure what happened with your order, but this is not our typical review. After looking into our order system, we see that you ordered your peppermint stick mocha with someone who was also unhappy with their cappuccino and bagel. We'd like to make things right for you. Please give our store a call back so that we can issue a refund and hopefully make your day a bit better.

reviews_data.review_text:
Mediocre is being nice.  Smallest size of coffee is 16 ounces.  Guess what I got in my cappuccino, one shot of espresso and 13 ounces of warm milk.   Mmmm I love warm milk and barely a hint of coffee.  Ordered an extra toasted bagel and cream cheese, guess what I got.  A chewy basic grocery store bagel that had not one bit of toastiness to it and NO cream cheese. Didnt figure this out until I was down the road or i would have asked for a refund.
Unclear what their business model is but someone needs to revisit it.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Not sure what happened with your order, but this is obviously not our typical review.   Since you’re too far gone for us to do anything about remaking your order, please give our store a call back so that we can issue a refund and hopefully make your day a bit better.

reviews_data.review_text: Perfect spot to grab coffee and something for breakfast/lunch. Large assortment of beverages making it better than Starbucks. Love their taxedo muffin and donut holes.
What a neat place!  First time visit, EXCELLENT coffee and friendly service.  Do yourself a favor and check them out.
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Thanks so much for the great review David!  Really appreciate it and can't wait for the next time that you bring you son in for a coffee!

Just let us know how we can make that time special for you!

John

reviews_data.review_text: Excellent service we would come more often but I would be broke all the time lol
reviews_data.owner_answer:
Michael... thanks so much for the great review!  We're looking forward to seeing you again, but remember that we usually have some kind of deal going every day.  2 for Tuesday (BOGO 4 $1) and $5 Fridays (any standard drink, any size for $5) are usually big hits for our customers.

Thanks again!

John

reviews_data.review_text: Best & most hospitable coffeshop management ever!
Amazing!!
reviews_data.owner_answer:
So appreciated Stephanie!  Please let us know what we can do to keep earning your business!

Be sure to always ask, "What's your Daily Deal?" every time you come in.

We look forward to serving you!

John

reviews_data.review_text: Extremely clean - my food and coffee were great! Staff was super friendly.
The cold brew here is my favorite especially with some sweet foam. The staff here is engaging and makes every experience personable.

Glad to have Biggby in the area. The Coffee is great, and the food is delicious! It’s nice being able to customize any drink/flavors. What really makes this place special are the amazing staff and owners!!
Absolutely delicious!
I loved this place! I ordered 3 drinks and a food beverage and they were delicious. The workers there were very nice and would recommend this place to anyone if all ages!
New and clean

The place was desolate, but I figured I would check it out anyway. They loaded my lattee with whipped cream and that was my first sign they were hiding the taste of the coffee, but it was horrible. Tasted burnt and old like it was just coffee that had been sitting there for days. Not impressed. The only reason I gave two stars was because the barista that helped me was very sweet, but I tossed the $7 coffee in the trash at my next stop.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Kayla, we’re so sorry to hear that you didn’t enjoy your Biggby experience. We pride ourselves on quality coffee (with or without whipped cream on top!). We’d love to make this right for you and help you find a drink you’ll love. Our brewed coffees, americanos, cappuccinos, etc sound like they may be more akin to your taste! Please stop on by anytime, and let us make this right.

reviews_data.review_text: I’m a military veteran also military veteran discounts. Found a hair in my bagel, when I asked for it to be remade John told me that was not possible and said that I put the hair in my own food.
Went in they changed their hours are I open till 7 Monday thru Sat and only till 6 on Sunday so hopefully my edit worked
Very kind and fast!
Coffee was great. Staff was super friendly.
We went for the first time and each got a coffee drink and shared a Bagel sandwich. The coffee, sandwich, and service were all great and we will go again soon!
So nice to have a good alternative to Starbucks.

I’ve only ordered delivery - however, these bagels are SO good. The customer service is also great, I love when employees write notes for the customers. I may be developing a Biggby addiction.

I was recently there and I live close to the area about six months ago. I know the owners John and Melissa and new associates were very friendly fast day get everybody’s orders in a timely manner and the coffee is probably some of the best coffee out there it’s better than the other companies like Starbucks and other companies
Great coffee, and customer service. Very friendly nice staff.
Absolutely so cute and the staff is so helpful! Would go every day ❤️

Dead dull place with dead dull employees. Ordered a regular coffee and staff had to make a new pot but never said anything. And where in the hell is the sugar? Was going to sit down and work but horrible experience changed my dine in to a to go.

I ordered a Peppermint Stick Mocha Latte and it was very good. I had it made with oat milk. Loved the candy cane crunchies on top of the whip. Also, the hubby bought a coffee and they have the best refill prices and are environmentally friendly. Also, comfortable inside. Employee was super friendly.

Absolutely delicious coffee. Get a frozen caramel marvel latte. You will never be disappointed.

Friendly staff as well!

Both yummy choices!

reviews_data.review_text: I stayed there for 2 days and I went to BIGGBY Coffee for 2 days. It was soooo good!!!!I wish there could be a store near where I live.

They used my free drink reward for the second drink. The problems list is too long for the coffee.
Love this BIGGBY location.
Kelsey and a friendly young gentleman took excellent care of me while I was in today.  The shop has a clean and welcoming atmosphere, and my drink was delicious!
Coffee is ok but never try the GOOD TO GO at this place because they will just give you couple cups of coffee ONLY so not worth it

Omg i love this place. I don’t even drink coffee that much but since they moved in to town I’m there two to three times a week. I love the frozen teddy bear or butter bear and the everything turkey cheese bagel is delicious. On top of that the customer service has always been above and beyond. You have a great team working there.

reviews_data.review_text: Wanted to say that Melissa at Biggby Coffee in Pineville cares about giving back to her local community as she donates to help out a little league team in Pineville thru Hope Soccer.  On behalf of Hope Soccer, we are very grateful for the impact Biggby has on our local kids! As a consumer of any service, I know that I look for businesses who are involved in their local community, such as Biggby Coffee! Also, I can tell you personally that their coffee and their bagel sandwiches are great!  Highly recommend!
Supper good whenever we go out of town we look for a biggby coffee it never disappoints this location was definitely my favorite staff was amazing thank you so much for everything 😊

Visited recently because I got an ad on Facebook and it’s so close to my house. I always love trying new coffee shops even though it can be hit or miss. This was definitely a hit though! I love that my latte has a nice sweet flavor while also being able to taste the espresso. I think they do a fantastic job balancing the sweetener to coffee ratio. I ordered a caramel marshmallow iced latte and loved it.

My boyfriend stopped in to grab us coffee again today and I got the same drink, and it tasted the same as when I got it the other day so they’re definitely consistent. We also tried the donut holes last time we visited, and those were great too.

The staff was super friendly and chatty with customers which is always nice to see anywhere you go. We will definitely come again in the future and make this our new go to spot.
Had a very pleasant experience visiting Biggby Coffee this morning! Customer service was phenomenal and very quick. The coffee itself was even better. Will definitely be coming back soon!

Ordered through DoorDash and was pleasantly surprised. The cold brew was incredible and the bagel was just as amazing, if not better! I love that they serve their bagels into the afternoon, most places don’t do that.

Disappointed with the coffee at the Waffle House, I headed here and spent an hour this morning sipping away at a small coffee that was actually the size of a small oil drum while I wrote a couple Yelp reviews. There's a very comfy single-seat booth in the back that was pretty darned awesome with a power outlet and a nice view of the comings and goings.

The coffee was excellent and the space was lovely.

The BEST cold foam ever. Very sweet staff and I’m so glad that they have weekly deals!

reviews_data.review_text: Great coffee and some yummy doughnuts

reviews_data.review_text: Always an awesome treat I get 2-3 times a week, excellent staff and smiles all around, love biggby coffee !!

Tired of weak Dunkin? Weary of burnt Starbucks? Biggby coffee is fresh and smooth! They carry everything from traditional blends to very creative latte drinks. The atmosphere is welcoming and friendly - if a bit small. Highly recommend!
This place is incredible! Great customer service, great environment, and super clean store! The drinks are incredible and always so yummy! Support your local business!!

I've been to this location multiple times, and the menu looks so exciting with multiple flavor options and most of them available in sugar free. I love creative mixes for my lattes, but it always falls very flat here. At Starbucks, they lack variety especially in sugar-free, but when they put syrup in you can taste it. You can taste it too much and as a matter of fact at Starbucks I always tell them to do half of the amount of syrup they normally do, so I'm not a person that likes an over sugary and syrupy drink. I'm writing this review because at this location, even though they have such cool interesting sounding drinks, you can't taste the syrup at all. It tastes like drinking espresso with warmed milk and a little tiny bit of sweetener, but no flavor whatsoever. I guess if I return to try their coffee, I'm going to have to ask for additional pumps and then watch it be too sweet would be my luck. Again, I'm really happy with all the flavor combinations offered here but you can't taste it.
reviews_data.owner_answer: Hi Ginger. Thank you for the feedback. Our baristas are very knowledgable about our menu and different syrups and would love to help you find the perfect balance between sweetness and flavor. If you stop in again, feel free to ask about a certain latte's sweetness or how the barista would make it for themselves! We'd love the chance to wow you with our variety of flavors :)

reviews_data.review_text: Great place for coffee, and very friendly staff.
Great coffee!
Fabulous customer service. We were first timers and the young lady explained the different drinks and answered all of our questions. Definitely will be back and will spread the word.

reviews_data.owner_answer: Terri, thanks for stopping by. We would love for you to give us a 2nd chance. May I recommend next time getting one less shot of espresso in your iced vanilla latte? reviews_data.review_text: The coffee is great and the staff is even nicer. Really a great place to see how a business should be ran

reviews_data.review_text: The drink I had was amazing!! Hands down better than most. The Asiago bagel with cream cheese was tough to chew and fairly dry. I wish I could have had more cream cheese because I could barely taste it. From now on I will just order the frozen coffee

reviews_data.review_text: Great Food, Great Coffee. Wonderful doordash experience with a personal note inside.

reviews_data.review_text: Clean, modern, bright coffee shop with very friendly staff and decent coffee. Has a drive through also.

So, this is only my second review ever, I don’t usually do this but it’s almost been a year they’ve been open and they deserve this! I’ve gone to Biggby for years back home (was so excited when they opened here!!) and have been in love with their sweet foam cold brew which is the best ever made, hands down! What makes the experience the best is the people here. John and Melissa are amazing and go above and beyond to make sure everyone is happy and enjoying their coffee (even when I can be a pain!) and you build a relationship with the rest of the staff when you go every day. They treat you like family and you know each other on a first name basis, which you don’t get very often in the world. Everyone I bring coffee to at my work absolutely loves their coffee and they all look forward to $5 Friday! I would give them 100 stars if I could but I’m limited to 5 so I will end with this… I love Biggby coffee no matter where I go but what makes this one special and the absolute best is the owners and the people who are making our coffee everyday. I appreciate y'all and thank y'all for everything!
I love getting coffee here before going to the Miller flea market next to it
reviews_data.owner_answer: Excellent! We are glad to be a convenient shop for you to help you enjoy your weekends:)

Absolutely delicious!

New and clean

Please stop on by anytime, and let us make this right.

To add to that, there was barely ANY cream cheese so I essentially just got a bagel with no topping.  I chalked it up to a one time thing and returned a couple days later. Today, I got an everything bagel with bacon egg and cheese. I struggled to get a bite out of it it was so hard. Oddly enough, the bottom was salvageable and I was able to eat that but the top was so hard it made my teeth hurt. I'm not sure if the bagels were stale or what but I've never had an experience like that with a bagel. Too many inconsistencies.

Please call or text me at 704.584.9399 so I can find out how to give you a 5-star experience from here on out!

I hope that the rest of your day is the BEST of your day!

John

reviews_data.review_text: Perfectly blended drinks

reviews_data.review_text: Super clean, friendly and wonderful coffee stop!  Highly recommend!

reviews_data.review_text: Stopped by when I was in the area, traveling for business. We don’t have Biggby locations in Asheville where I’m from. Both my coworker and I were very satisfied. I tried both the “campfire” cold brew and also another blue raspberry flavored drink with crystal boba. Really can’t wait to go back!

reviews_data.review_text: drinks are so good food is good veryyyy underrated the workers are so nice 1000000/10

reviews_data.review_text: Really good breakfast sandwiches
reviews_data.owner_answer: Thanks for stopping in Chris! We're so glad you love our Bragels!
